h3 States

p.c-text Textareas has three states vailable:

ul.c-text
  li success: <code>c-input--success</code>
  li warning: <code>c-input--warning</code>
  li danger: <code>c-input--danger</code>

.c-mb4.c-mt2
  div(style="max-width:60rem")
    textarea.c-input.c-input--success Sample text

  :code(lang="html")
    <textarea class="c-input c-input--success">
      Sample text
    </textarea>

.c-mb4.c-mt2
  div(style="max-width:60rem")
    textarea.c-input.c-input--warning Sample text

  :code(lang="html")
    <textarea class="c-input c-input--warning">
      Sample text
    </textarea>

.c-mb4.c-mt2
  div(style="max-width:60rem")
    textarea.c-input.c-input--danger Sample text

  :code(lang="html")
    <textarea class="c-input c-input--danger">
      Sample text
    </textarea>

